        "timestamp": "2020-11-12 12:39:16.000000000",
        "message": "Patch Set 1:\n\nAlternatively we could remove encoding entirely, as this is not the first time it has caused issues. \n\nEncoding was added to handle a use cases where resource resolution would resolve a URL which could contain whitespaces. The proper solution for this would be to add another resource in the cba, which uses a script to encode the URL.\n\nLet me know your thoughts.",
        "patchset_number": 1
      },
